ites? With the growing interest in popularity of cooking, we've had great success with our interactive cooking events. Foodies and non-foodies alike have given us very positive feedback.</p><p>Rap or rock, classical or show tunes. polka bands or big bands - we can provide the kind of music that really moves you and your guests.</p><p>No location is too far away or too far out for our remote catering services. From a Pacific Island to the Pyrenees to Palm Beach, we can plan and manage your event from our headquarters or yours. Distance, language, logistics - none of them present problems. We've done remote catering in locations all over the world.</p></div><div id="footer"><p><a href="services/events/">Event Planning</a> | <a href="services/weddings/">Weddings</a> | <a href="services/wineandfood/">Wine &amp; Food</a> | <a href="services/clambakes/">Clam Bakes</a></p><p><a href="info/about/">About Us</a> | <a href="info/locations/">Locations</a> | <a href="info/photos/">Photo Gallery</a> | <a href="info/clients/">Clients</a> | <a href="info/affiliates/">Affiliates</a> | <a href="info/press/">Press</a> | <a href="info/calendar/">Calendar</a> | <a href="info/contact/">Contact</a> | </p><p>&copy; 2005 Black Tie Caterers. All Rights Reserved.</p></div></div></body></html>